Author: SooEz4Me
Title: [BOUNTY] üîù‚≠ï‚≠ï‚≠ï MAMBOCOIN |üíé HUGE BOUNTY REWARDS!!! ‚úîÔ∏è
Body: WEBSITE | Twitter | Facebook | VK | Telegram | Medium     General rules    Bounty campaign will be held in two stages. Time of bounty campaign from 30.07.2018 to 30.09.2018 and the second stage: 15.10.2018 to 10.11.2018.  Bounty pool is determined in amount of 3% of total sale of tokens  The participants of the bounty campaign for their performance are awarded the tokens of the project Mambocoin(mbc) 1 mbc = $0.16 for Pre-ICO price  Bounty hunter chooses one or several areas of participation for himself, taking into account the compliance of his accounts, the requirements of participation in the campaign.  Bounty hunter must register for each chosen direction of participation by filling out and sending the registration form in relevant section of the campaign.  Confirmation of user registration to participate in the bounty campaign, is a letter from administration of the campaign, sent from the email support@mb24.io, which refers to the possibility of participation of a particular profile in the selected bounty program.     In order to simplify the accounting and accrual of stakes, time of the bounty campaign is divided into 9 periods (for the first stage).   Period 1: from 13th August to 19th August 2018; Period 2: from 20th August to 26th August 2018; Period 3: from 27th August to 2nd September 2018; Period 4: from 3rd September to 9th September 2018; Period 5: from 10th September to 16th September 2018; Period 6: from 17th September to 23th September 2018; Period 7: from 24th September to 30th September 2018;  Second stage  Period 1: from 8th October to 14th October 2018; Period 2: from 15th October to 21th October 2018; Period 3: from 22th October to 28th October 2018; Period 4: from 29th October to 4th November 2018; Period 5: from 5th November to 10th November 2018;    All bounty pool is 3% of the total token sale amount at the Pre-ICO stage.  Video/Media/Article - 22% Telegram - 20% Facebook - 20% Twitter - 15 % Translation - 23%        To participate in this campaign, you must register on the website http://mb24.io/ by clicking ‚ÄúGet tokens‚Äù  You can join the campaign at any time (before November 10th, 2018)by filling out the form and sending it no later than two days before the start of new period.  Translations must be made by the user himself, the use of Google translator (and other automatic translation systems) will result in disqualification.  Link to the translation should be added to the "Report" section in your account on the website http://mb24.io/. After verification you will accrued stakes.       Translation Whitepaper - 800 tokens (Korean, Chinese, Arabic, Spanish, French, German,Fillipino, Brazilian, Italian, Thai, Turkish, Japanese, Vietnamese)  Translation conditions of bounty campaign - 600 tokens (only from Russian into English)  Translation lending - 600 tokens (Korean, Chinese, Arabic, Spanish, French, German, Brazilian, Italian, Thai, Turkish, Japanese, Fillipino, Vietnamese)   English speaking users may write in this telegram: https://t.me/eaxale  Russian speaking users may write in this telegram: https://t.me/Karina_Uysal          To participate in this campaign, you must register on the website http://mb24.io/ by clicking ‚ÄúGet tokens‚Äù  You can join the campaign at any time (before November 10th, 2018) by filling out the form and sending it no later than two days before the start of new period.  Participants must subscribe to the project page, put at least 3 likes and make at least 3 reposts materials of the official project page per week.  Official project page: link  The post is considered unique if the uniqueness of the text at least 80% (check on Advego.ru.) If this figure is lower, the post is equal to the usual repost.  When writing a post, you must provide a link to official website of the project - http://mb24.io/  Only constructive posts are counted. Off-topic spam and posting are not counted and lead to disqualification from participation in the campaign.  If during the bounty campaign, the user's facebook account is closed, blocked or deleted, the user is disqualified.
